> # Show execute subcommand help
> composio tools execute --help
composio

composio 0.1.24

USAGE

$ execute [(-d, --data text)] [--user-id text] [--connected-account-id text] [--too
lkit-version text] <slug>

DESCRIPTION

Execute a tool by slug with JSON arguments.

ARGUMENTS

<slug>

  A user-defined piece of text.

  Tool slug (e.g. "GITHUB_CREATE_ISSUE")

OPTIONS

(-d, --data text)

  A user-defined piece of text.

  JSON arguments, @file, or - for stdin

  This setting is optional.

--user-id text

  A user-defined piece of text.

────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
